FILE HAS BEEN INSPECTED 19.11.25

- Start
- Explore Dungeon
- Participate in events
- Kill the boss
- Get Loot
- Sell Loot / Buy some random items
- Choose extra Perk/Talant/Gear
- Die
- Go to the starting point and do minor upgrades for dark energy you got during last run
- Become stronger
- Repeat

Combat Game Loop (Short Game Loop):
- Hit
- Use Flask
- Win
- Collect the loot
- Repeat

Dungeon Game Loop (Medium Game Loop):
- Enter new room
- Explore
- Repeat

Game Loop Across Different Runs (Long Game Loop):
- Enter the dungeon
- Die
- Become Stronger
- Repeat
